## 3. Project Conventions

### Job State Machine

`'extracting'` → `'extraction_complete'` → `'generating'` → `'generation_complete'` → `'complete'`

### API Endpoints Reference

| Endpoint                      | Method | Purpose                           | Critical Notes                            |
| ----------------------------- | ------ | --------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| `/api/status`                 | GET    | System health (CUDA, voice count) | Required for Step 0 UI                    |
| `/api/upload`                 | POST   | File upload                       | Returns `job_id` + `filename`             |
| `/api/process/extract`        | POST   | Start extraction                  | `{"job_id": "..."}`                       |
| `/api/book/speakers?job_id=X` | GET    | Extract characters                | Must pass `job_id` query param            |
| `/api/voices`                 | GET    | List available voices             | Returns voice registry                    |
| `/api/voice-assignments`      | POST   | Save voice mappings               | `{"job_id": "...", "assignments": {...}}` |
| `/api/generate`               | POST   | Start TTS generation              | `{"job_id": "...", "settings": {...}}`    |
| `/api/jobs/<job_id>`          | GET    | Poll job status                   | Returns complete job state                |
| `/api/audio/combine`          | POST   | Combine clips to M4B              | `{"job_id": "..."}`                       |
| `/api/download/<filename>`    | GET    | Download `.m4b`                   | Path traversal check required             |

### React Component State (`VoxNovelUI_v2.js`)

- `step`: 0 (check) → 1 (upload) → 2 (extract) → 2.5 (voices) → 3 (generate) → 3.5 (review) → 4 (download)
- `jobId`, `characters`, `voiceAssignments`, `logs`

