```

### Manual API Testing

```bash
curl -s http://localhost:3000/api/status | jq .           # Via proxy
curl -s http://localhost:5000/api/status | jq              # Direct Flask
```

### Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue                    | Root Cause              | Fix                                                |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| "Cannot connect to API"  | Flask not running       | Start Flask: `python backend/voxnovel_api.py`      |
| React crash on voices    | Wrong API format        | Return `{code: "English"}` not nested              |
| Only "Narrator" detected | Not using BookNLP       | Check `.quotes` file exists                        |
| TTS very slow            | Model loaded every call | Use AudioWorker persistent engine                  |
| ngrok offline            | Wrong syntax            | Use v3: `ngrok http 3000 --authtoken=X --domain=Y` |

